Description: Kramer 600ST Electric Guitar Floyd Rose Seymour Duncan American Made Rare.Guitar has it's fair share of nicks and dings, which i will go over, and can be seen in the photos. Electronics are fully functional. Starting at the top, there are some cracks in the clear coat on the backside of the neck where the bolts for the lock downs go through. Some very small finish cracks where the neck meets the body. Upper horn has about 1/4" chunk out of the finish. Lower horn has about a 1/2" chunk out of the finish, and a piece that's down to the wood on the face. The base of the body has four chunks from 1/4" to about 3/4". Two of the knobs are not original.
